videos.description: After a wild scramble on the floor, Houston comes up with the ball and takes it the other way as DeJon Jarreau rises up for an impressive layup while absorbing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jarreau's acrobatic and-1 pumps up the Houston crowd) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Jarreau's acrobatic and-1 pumps up the Houston crowd

videos.description: With less than 30 seconds remaining in the half, Justin Gorham pulls up for a 3-pointer and misses but Brison Gresham is there for a Houston tip-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Houston's Gresham tips in teammate's miss seconds before half) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Houston's Gresham tips in teammate's miss seconds before half

videos.description: Caleb Mills starts the second half off hot as he continues to drain 3s from beyond the arc vs. Tulsa.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Houston's hustle results in a Mills 3-pointer) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Houston's hustle results in a Mills 3-pointer

videos.description: Caleb Mills pulls up from the corner over his Tulsa defender to drain two  more to stay hot in the second half, scoring the first 19 points for Houston out of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mills knocks in the first 19 points of the half for Houston) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Mills knocks in the first 19 points of the half for Houston

videos.description: Frank Haith is ejected in the second half of action vs. Houston after he receives his second technical foul for arguing a call with the officials.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tulsa head coach ejected with second tech arguing call) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Tulsa head coach ejected with second tech arguing call

videos.description: Caleb Mills drives through Tulsa's defense and lays in a shot while falling to the hardwood to cap off his career performance in Houston's win.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mills slices and dices through Tulsa's defense for sweet layup) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Mills slices and dices through Tulsa's defense for sweet layup
